EL1-5e: Troublesome. I may have dreamed last night.
VEX: Oh? What of?
EL1-5e: Something dark. Something all-encompassing, and inevitable. It’s hard to describe. I felt. . . fear.
VEX: We all have nightmares from time to time. 
