title: Dialogue7
---
<<showCG 0>>
<<setRobo roboNeutral>>
EL1-5e: I assume it from the way you speak.
<<setVex vexNeutral>>
VEX: Oh, I suppose ASCO’s engineers speak a little more smarty-pants than I do, hmm?
<<setRobo roboBlush>>
EL1-5e: Ehehehe. . . not exactly.
EL1-5e: I quite enjoy your personality, actually. Which is not a customer-service lie, by the way.
<<setVex vexNeutral>>
VEX: Aha, how reassuring.
<<setVex vexGlasses>>
VEX: Alright, morning calibration complete. It’s time to get in the weeds, EL1-5e. Are you ready?
<<setRobo roboNeutral>>
EL1-5e: With you as my guide.
<<startDay 2>>
<<endDialogue end>>
